# Monitoring Guide

## Components

This monitoring stack includes:

- Prometheus
- Grafana
- Node Exporter
- AlertManager

## Access

Grafana:
http://localhost:3000

Prometheus:
http://localhost:9090

## Metrics

Prometheus collects metrics from:

- Node Exporter
- Application services
- Databases

## Alerts

AlertManager processes alerts generated by Prometheus rules.

## Dashboards

Grafana dashboards visualize:

- Infrastructure metrics
- Application metrics
- Database performance